  "remarks": "Yulia Belekhova is a member of the Presidential Council for Civil Society and Human Rights, and chairwoman of the Council’s working group on the so-called “special military operation” (war of aggression) in Ukraine. She is also head of the Moscow regional branch of the pro-Putin All-Russia People’s Front. She backed Russia’s war of aggression against Ukraine and participated in propaganda events in support of the war.",
